attributes.title: Worst app!!🍊🍅🐖🤷‍♀️
attributes.review: I was definitely SOOOOO excited to download this app after reading all the “great” reviews and hearing about what an “amazing” president he is on “real” news broadcast ‘Fox News’!!😁 And I wanted to give it 5 stars but when I tell you I was DISAPPOINTED I mean VERY DISAPPOINTED!😡It started the second I tried to open the app, it literally took 3 1/2 HOURS to download.😕As soon as I was able to open the app I jumped outta my bed of fright..😰I got so scared after seeing a very PLUMP like orange scaly wigged man in the center of my screen holding up an extremely wrinkly fist.. 🍊😭it had to be the most horrid facial expression I have ever SEEN!!😖😣 Sadly that wasn’t even the worst part.. After being traumatized for hours I went back to the app to see what all the fuss was abt but I made sure to stay clear of the creep orange pic🍊👋.. I was only able to browse the app for 30 seconds before it froze and kicked me out (keep in my my phone is updated and this hasn’t happen for any of my other apps)! 😕 I tried to tap the app again and it froze and brought back to home screen after 20 seconds like WHAT!? I quickly put a number in and it said invalid!! But it’s an accurate number😭 so I kept trying with the apps 20 sec timer then at one point it said “too many attempt proceeding to copy all background information on phone and send it to higher law for processing and deleting” that’s when I said HELL NAH and deleted the app.. 😭👋 I mean I REALLLY tried to be happy with this app but this app made it absolutely impossible and it’s as if every single chance I tried to give it to accept the app and Trump it DENIED! so I’ll take that as a sign and leave.. by the way the orange scaly man still terrifies me to this DAY!😖👏✨🍅🍊
